snippet.title: Best VGM 1090 - Mario Party - Rainbow Castle
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1876 - https://youtu.be/0EhiDgp8Drg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Mario Party (1998)
Rainbow Castle
Yasunori Mitsuda
